    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require lifetime restraining orders for convicts of domestic violence offences",
        "additional_details": "We want to stop domestic violence victims and their children being victimised or killed by the perpetrator of the abuse. We believe they should have the right to not live in fear for their lives. Far too many victims are killed each year through lack of protection and it needs to stop.",
        "background": "We want the Government to require lifetime restraining orders for people convicted of domestic violence offences.",
